info:
Responsibilities：
	Assist project leader on digital transformation scheme preparation, including business understanding, business design, benchmark studying, application planning etc.
	Assist the manager to prepare all kinds of delivery documents and basic analysis on project base;
	Compile Market and competitor research and review;
	Support Admin and logistics for Team operations, meeting and workshop internally and externally;
	Financial support: Independently responsible for the whole PO process, communicate with vendors, follow up the payment and other internal functions;

Job Requirement
	Fulltime students from top universities. Prior experience in business environment will be a plus
Strong analytical and learning ability, strong logical expression ability and innovative mind, able to quickly learn and innovate analytics on fast changing marketing. Love the retail FMCG industry
	Excellent communication skills in English
Fast learners, analytical thinking and Strong team spirit
	At least 4 days/week attendance for at least four months

职责描述：
1.负责用户关系建立和维护,与用户建立长期稳定的伙伴关系,不断提升客户对蔚来的忠诚度; 
2.用户体验管理:提供空间体验、内容体验、礼品兑换、餐饮体验、用车相关等全场景体验管理,确保用户体验超越期待: 
3.负责用户成长、用户关系深耕、用户社群维护:协助用户解决相关问题,情感协助用户关系的深耕,不断提升用户满意度以及用户活跃度;
4.执行和跟进体验门店的日常运营,包括但不限于吧台、儿童区等; 
5.负责总体策划并落地蔚来中心内车主用户体验产品,丰富车主体验; 
6.协同落地标准体验产品以及产品效果评估。
任职要求：
1.26届及之后本科及以上学历,专业不限 
2.对新能源电动汽车具有强烈兴趣,善于快速了解新产品和新功能; 
3.有一定的活动策划经验及规划执行能力,能够主持沙龙活动; 
4.保持精力充沛,在非常活跃的环境中提供出色的用户体验; 
5.拥有较强的文字功底、丰富的内容创作经验,优秀的沟通能力; 
6.熟练使用word、excel等办公软件
